<view class="wrap"><scroll-view class="scroll_view" scroll-x="true"><view class="list"><block wx:for="{{list}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="index"><block><image class="cover" src="{{item.img}}" mode="aspectFill" lazy-load="true"></image></block></block></view></scroll-view><view class="up_img_title">上传图片<text class="small">{{"/限"+maxNum+"张"}}</text></view><view class="image_list"><block wx:for="{{data.images}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="index"><view class="item"><image class="cover" src="{{item}}" mode="aspectFill" lazy-load="true"></image><image class="del" data-index="{{index}}" src="../../static/icon_del.png" mode="aspectFit" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['del',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e"></image></view></block><block wx:if="{{data.images.length<maxNum}}"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['upImage',['$event']]]]]}}" class="item" bindtap="__e"><image class="cover" src="../../static/btn_addimage.png" mode="aspectFill"></image></view></block></view><view class="tips"><text class="color_main">*</text>请按要求填写并上传（文字不能漏填，照片张数不能少，否则无法为您提供设计服务）</view><view class="btns"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['upTemp',['$event']]]]]}}" class="btn color_main" bindtap="__e">自己上传</view><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['start',['$event']]]]]}}" class="btn bg_main" bindtap="__e">开始设计</view></view></view>